column11:
  {\small In this paper we define and we study properties of}
$\left(l,1,p+2q,q\cdot l\right) -$ {\small numbers,} $\left(l,1,p+2q,q\cdot
l\right) -$ {\small quaternions,} $\left(l,1,p+2q,q\cdot l\right) -$ {\small
symbol elements. Finally, we obtain an algebraic structure with these
elements.}
